thread.title: Bonnie

author: Bonnie
title: Bonnie
text: This Christmas I asked for a choir folder from this company because several of my chorale friend had one. The one I got was too large for my purpose. I emailed and we dealt with the exchange very quickly. I got a new folder in just a few days. With it arrived a return postage sticker for me to send back the too-big folder. It all took only a few days. Amazing!
